│  55 /// execute once for every X iterations of the loop header so the block   │
│ should                                                                        │
│  56 /// only contribute 1/X of its cost to the total cost calculation, but    │
│ when                                                                          │
│  57 /// optimizing for code size it will just be 1 as code size costs don't   │
│ depend                                                                        │
