ScalableVF (minimum lane counts) immediately after they are computed, and adding
a defensive check before VFRange construction, we restore the invariant relied
upon throughout vectorization planning and eliminate the assertion crash. The fix
is minimally invasive, backward-compatible, and safeguards against future target
